                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-659126550" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-659126550" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="659126550">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/baronontree/">树上的男爵</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-04-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">尽管翻译不尽如人意，还是强烈推荐。一个在实践中发展着的当代毛主义革命纲领，读来激动人心啊！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
